        <a href="/albums" class='w-100'><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512143889056-b57b4153f038?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" class='w-100'></a>     </div>
